tron and\npositron scattering. The final ratio of positron to electron scattering:\n$R=1.027\\pm0.005\\pm0.05$ for $<Q^2>=0.206$ GeV$^2$ and $0.830\\leq \\epsilon\\leq\n0.943$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Jun 2013 19:09:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 10 Jul 2013 18:10:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-09-04"}
