 will also establish firmly the cumulative impact of powerful\nradio galaxies on the evolution of baryons from the epoch of group/cluster\nformation to the present day.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Jun 2013 20:00:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-06-12"}
