mplication of Schrodinger's formula for DNA sequencing is\ndiscussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Jun 2013 03:35:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 5 Aug 2013 21:57:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-08-23"}
