 the V/R\nvariation appeared in around 2007, which looks like a recurrence of the\nprevious event, we found less developed state of the disk without appreciable\ntime lag.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Jun 2013 13:01:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-16"}
